metadata.name: Ares
metadata.description:
Meet Ares, the god of war, who was worshipped for his might but remembered for the protection he offered to those in need.  

Ares reminds us that while righteous anger and powerful passions can be life-changing and inspiring, they must also be balanced so as not to cause destruction.

The art summons the spirit of battle, capturing the intense emotions that Ares represents.
